{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dbf9e1d6bf","title":"关于停战抗日的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7636f7fd80","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":15,"articleId":"dbf9e1d6bf"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui1","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1913-1943卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui1a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"db36274fe1","type":"title","text":"关于停战抗日的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"dbf9e1d6bf"},{"id":"449b1579cc","type":"paragraph","text":"苏维埃中央政府与人民红军军事委员会，现已发布命令：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"dbf9e1d6bf"},{"id":"50e8ec80e0","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）一切红军部队停止对国民党革命军之任何攻击行动；","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"dbf9e1d6bf"},{"id":"aa6e9f0ca9","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）仅在被攻击时，允许釆取必须之自卫手段；","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"dbf9e1d6bf"},{"id":"4ba04eaefc","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）凡属国民革命军，因其向我进攻而被缴获之人员武器，在该军抗日时，一律送还，其愿当红军者听便。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"dbf9e1d6bf"},{"id":"c702e8047c","type":"subdate","text":"（四）如果国民革命军向抗日阵地转移时，制止任何防碍举动，并愿给","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"dbf9e1d6bf"},{"id":"32c12f5437","type":"paragraph","text":"以一切可能之援助。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"dbf9e1d6bf"},{"id":"187d478999","type":"paragraph","text":"吾人已决定再行恳切申请一切国民革命军部队与南京政府，与吾人停战携手抗日。该项申请书，已在草拟中。目前察晋绥三省形势．已属危急万状，吾人极愿与南京政府合作，以达援绥抗日救亡图存之目的，如南京政府诚能顾念国难，停止内战出兵抗日，苏维埃愿以全力援助，并愿以全国之红军主力为先锋，与日寇决一死战。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"dbf9e1d6bf"}],"page":{"id":"88f9025fc9","publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"dbf9e1d6bf","start":301,"end":301}}}},"__N_SSG":true}